dct_title_s:
L'Afrique Dreſsée ſur les Observations de Mrs. de l'Academie Royale
          des Sciences et quelques autres; & ſur les Memoires les plus recens
dct_description_sm:
Retains the geographical features of L'Isle's map of 1700 (see NOR 0059). Title across
        top: Africa Accurate in Imperia, Regna, Status and Populos Divisa, ad Usum Serenissimi
        Bourgundiae Ducis. Dedicated to the Duke to Burgundy; Prime meridian through Ferro
        Island.
dct_rights_sm: Image from the Dr. Oscar I. Norwich collection of maps of Africa and its islands, 1486 - ca. 1865 courtesy Stanford University Libraries. This item is in the public domain. There are no restrictions on use. If you have questions, please contact the David Rumsey Map Center at rumseymapcenter@stanford.edu.
